==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stipe
<hw>Stipe</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>stipes</ets> a
stock, post, branch: cf. F. <ets>stipe</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>The stalk or petiole of a frond, as of a fern.</def>
<sd>(b)</sd> <def>The stalk of a pistil.</def> <sd>(c)</sd> <def>The
trunk of a tree.</def> <sd>(d)</sd> <def>The stem of a fungus or
mushroom.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

